test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 5 == 25
 +  where 5 = <built-in function prod>([5])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x75fc90db1040>([25])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x75fc90db1040> = [[1], [1, 25], [25, 1], [25, 1, 25], [1], [1, 25], ...].count
